{"tid":1053282,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"溝左好多年香港女仔，以下呢幾個特質一定走唔撚甩","createTime":"2019-03-09T02:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T07:00:18.000Z","uid":82389,"like":254,"dislike":433,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"77d7a6a4707c75743566366099c537a661d4d468","tid":1053282,"uid":82389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:31:33.000Z","msg":"1. 一句定生死。基本上唔係話講錯一句野<br />\n例如傻西瓜變咗傻閪嗰啲。<br />\n<br />\n而係例如講嘅嘢係佢冇乜興趣嘅，例如自己啲事。<br />\n通常就即刻唔覆 或者都好難傾得返落去<br />\n<br />\n（雖然呢個特質好多女仔都有，但係日本、台灣、就算係大陸妹都好、都起碼會敷衍下你<br />\n<br />\n2. 經常放飛機<br />\n<br />\n就算你早一個星期約佢都好啦<br />\n到早一日confirm佢又會話唔記得咗約咗你<br />\n<br />\n早兩三日約嘅話 又話唔得閒<br />\n即興約更加唔駛諗（又話覺得你唔尊重佢<br />\n有時真係覺得好撚誇張<br />\n<br />\n（其他國家嘅女仔，基本上除咗網絡騙案之外，乜乜乜買點數卡做雞嗰啲，否則一般約佢都會confirm到出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 睇唔起男人<br />\n<br />\n打從心底覺得你係狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（當然亦都因為香港太多男人係廢柴有關，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好心你哋唔好死溝爛溝，<br />\n<br />\n其實第三點先係最重要，因為如果個個都係咁諗嘅時候，意味着佢哋看待你唔會以一般社交關係嘅對等形式"},{"pid":"242c2ba524d49ed23f88bb310e5ff9ca3a790b2f","tid":1053282,"uid":140167,"like":591,"dislike":66,"score":525,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:33:56.000Z","msg":"Sor. 我女朋友你上面既 3 個特質完全無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bc2a2dd26fd19dc91a5d9400bd4b42665e3226","tid":1053282,"uid":7355,"like":250,"dislike":8,"score":242,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"其實係狗公造成"},{"pid":"55ec3a804fada8d80882cfaef29f4733a3919279","tid":1053282,"uid":182406,"like":487,"dislike":3,"score":484,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:35:25.000Z","msg":"對你無興趣咪咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3940debd25ce46f13527adc8dd650f0ccbe090","tid":1053282,"uid":146654,"like":297,"dislike":6,"score":291,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:46:25.000Z","msg":"如果樓主係靚仔就一啲唔會覺得香港女仔有呢啲特質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n單係第三點就唔成立啦 同埋靚仔仲會俾邊個放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca1de6b4083e4da75216a00d27447bfe34a26a1","tid":1053282,"uid":142212,"like":209,"dislike":6,"score":203,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:50:53.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係你嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f4cd22e14e32cdac2424bfb9040ebe31bc37a7","tid":1053282,"uid":136415,"like":154,"dislike":4,"score":150,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:06:13.000Z","msg":"頭兩個point咪就係對你個人無興趣先咁<br />\n同你講嘅野無關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日比人放飛機係人地唔好意思拒絕你啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1092df2f74ddf88621d71bac796231366aa95b0","tid":1053282,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":40,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:07:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思我溝親d女都對我好主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上識落頭15分鐘已經確定到有無火花，無既話你做乜都無撚用啦"},{"pid":"61e699aadded413fcc87cc11d267e4c617331f7e","tid":1053282,"uid":82389,"like":101,"dislike":14,"score":87,"quote":{"pid":"7e3940debd25ce46f13527adc8dd650f0ccbe090","tid":1053282,"uid":146654,"like":297,"dislike":6,"score":291,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:46:25.000Z","msg":"如果樓主係靚仔就一啲唔會覺得香港女仔有呢啲特質<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n單係第三點就唔成立啦 同埋靚仔仲會俾邊個放飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應約準時 赴約 呢d係基本禮貌 要靚仔先唔甩底 呢個社會真係大撚獲 講到樣衰比人甩底應份咁"},{"pid":"e642656d80669bdfcc7ef6f9c84a9558a823df92","tid":1053282,"uid":82389,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"a6f4cd22e14e32cdac2424bfb9040ebe31bc37a7","tid":1053282,"uid":136415,"like":154,"dislike":4,"score":150,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019